qrcode.min.js
  QRCode.js v1.0.0 — https://github.com/davidshimjs/qrcodejs
  Source: npm package `qrcodejs` 1.0.0, file `qrcode.min.js`
  License: MIT, Copyright (c) 2012 davidshimjs

To upgrade, replace the file with the same artifact from the newer npm
release and update the version noted here.
